	â€¢	Lead to confusion in incident/change/problem records
	â€¢	Cause inaccurate dependency maps in Service Mapping
	â€¢	Increase maintenance effort and inconsistency across modules
	â€¢	Block reconciliation and normalization for Discovery and ITOM

This effort prepares the CMDB for clean ingestion from ServiceNow Discovery by removing ITAM-based duplicates.


